overview.en: Quickest way to get into the exclusive presales of the most promising ICOs. Guaranteed best discounts to our token holders. The ICNQ token is a premium club access token. With this token you can be sure to participate in the ICOs of the escorted companies and get the biggest discount available during the ICO. As a rule, this is 15-30%. This means that owning 1% of all ICNQ tokens entitles you to buy 1% of issued startup tokens. In addition, you will receive up to 30% discount on the issue price. So you get with ICNQ a guaranteed participation at maximum discount. The tokens of the startups are not only available exclusively to ICNQ token holders, they only get the best conditions.
